# Compiled output
bin/
sources.txt
*.class

# Runtime data — the live database, store config, daily backups and generated
# files are per-install state, not source. The app recreates data/ on first run
# (seeds the catalogue, writes default store config, bootstraps an admin login),
# so a fresh clone starts clean. Real invoices, customers and password hashes
# must never live in version control — back them up via the app, not git.
data/
invoices/

# One-off safety copy of the pre-SQLite data taken during migration (real
# business data — never commit).
data_backup_pre_sqlite_migration/
